{"TopicId":61472,"ForumId":18,"TopicTitle":"Science of the Spheres - development","CreatedByName":"NovaSilisko","CreatedById":3897,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-01-29T10:14:46Z","PageNum":24,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"gmpd2000","CreatedById":37101,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-11T23:17:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GregroxMun\u0022 data-cite=\u0022GregroxMun\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E...Or, how about this? Pictures taken by spacecrafts can be printed as posters and hung on the wall!\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENova, I\u0027ll throw gold at you if you implement this.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-12T00:45:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022gmpd2000\u0022 data-cite=\u0022gmpd2000\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ENova, I\u0027ll throw gold at you if you implement this.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHe\u0027ll have plenty of gold, from mining it in the Microverse!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NovaSilisko","CreatedById":3897,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-12T01:03:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022gmpd2000\u0022 data-cite=\u0022gmpd2000\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ENova, I\u0027ll throw gold at you if you implement this.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI\u0027ll take that gold in advance if you don\u0027t mind.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NovaSilisko","CreatedById":3897,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-16T17:47:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://gfycat.com/ShockedBogusHare\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://gfycat.com/ShockedBogusHare\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBeginning of day/night cycle for headquarters scene. Still need to get a nice starfield texture, right now I\u0027m just using a tiled one.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Voidryder","CreatedById":57308,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-16T17:54:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EJust played around in the prototype a bit. Looks like it\u0027s going to be a winner. So if someone wanted to support your efforts with a modest donation, how would they go about that?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NovaSilisko","CreatedById":3897,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-16T19:58:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Voidryder\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Voidryder\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ESo if someone wanted to support your efforts with a modest donation, how would they go about that?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EWait a while, until there\u0027s some manner of official preorder thing set up. Donations are tricky to have, even if you put in huge red letters that donating doesn\u0027t entitle you to a copy of the game, people will think it does anyway. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-16T20:32:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NovaSilisko\u0022 data-cite=\u0022NovaSilisko\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://gfycat.com/ShockedBogusHare\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://gfycat.com/ShockedBogusHare\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBeginning of day/night cycle for headquarters scene. Still need to get a nice starfield texture, right now I\u0027m just using a tiled one.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIt\u0027s gotta be a real life one, but like with a super tiny change that no one would notice. Like, changing orion into something different.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Voidryder","CreatedById":57308,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-16T20:56:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NovaSilisko\u0022 data-cite=\u0022NovaSilisko\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EWait a while, until there\u0027s some manner of official preorder thing set up. Donations are tricky to have, even if you put in huge red letters that donating doesn\u0027t entitle you to a copy of the game, people will think it does anyway. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ECopy that. Wasn\u0027t expecting anything. Just wanted to help out a genius. But I\u0027ll wait until pre-order. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NovaSilisko","CreatedById":3897,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-19T03:31:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EDid up some lights that come on after the sun sets. Need to make proper sources for them, but...\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/kWJ5nx5.png\u0022 alt=\u0022kWJ5nx5.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E(still no real earth stars)\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EEdit: And a quick video of a sunrise \u003Ca href=\u0022http://gfycat.com/AnimatedCornyKouprey\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://gfycat.com/AnimatedCornyKouprey\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EStill at much accelerated time, final one will be real-time.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-02-19T07:06:36Z\u0022 title=\u002202/19/2015 07:06  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 19, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by NovaSilisko\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NovaSilisko","CreatedById":3897,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-21T07:54:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/P3Xicwk.jpg\u0022 alt=\u0022P3Xicwk.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EShelves!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Bill Phil","CreatedById":127797,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-21T08:53:41Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThis game looks promising! I hope all turns out well.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Voidryder","CreatedById":57308,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-21T12:40:26Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EHad to do a double take on those shelves. Thought they were the real deal on first scroll. Nice job.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"gmpd2000","CreatedById":37101,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-21T14:11:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EPhotorealistic shelves! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"carlpilot","CreatedById":130727,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-21T19:58:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENice work lately! One question, how are you creating procedural planets? \u003Ca href=\u0022https://planetverse.wordpress.com/2015/02/17/procedural-problem-generator/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMy attempt wasn\u0027t very good.\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E-Carlpilot \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NovaSilisko","CreatedById":3897,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-21T20:11:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022carlpilot\u0022 data-cite=\u0022carlpilot\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ENice work lately! One question, how are you creating procedural planets? \u003Ca href=\u0022https://planetverse.wordpress.com/2015/02/17/procedural-problem-generator/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EMy attempt wasn\u0027t very good.\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cp\u003E-Carlpilot \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EGenerally it\u0027s just a process of having multiple layers of noise blended together over either a fully procedural sphere, or a pre-made mesh sphere. For terrain textures, it\u0027s a matter of using vertex colors to blend together the different textures, and using a triplanar shader to make it map nicely onto a sphere.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EFor the terrain itself, look into Libnoise.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Dres","CreatedById":131150,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-22T03:00:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EJust started looking into this, and it looks very, very promising!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Czosnex","CreatedById":38038,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-24T19:03:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMe too! I\u0027m eager to play a more recent version too \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NovaSilisko","CreatedById":3897,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-24T20:18:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWriting up a big blog post about the recent development history and the current plan. Approaching 700 words and several images so far.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-02-24T20:25:05Z\u0022 title=\u002202/24/2015 08:25  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 24, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by NovaSilisko\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Andersenman","CreatedById":61273,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-25T11:14:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Etl;dr\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003Edl\u0027d.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NovaSilisko","CreatedById":3897,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-28T19:39:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/wEvpzsFW4MY?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"gmpd2000","CreatedById":37101,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-28T19:51:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NovaSilisko\u0022 data-cite=\u0022NovaSilisko\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo\u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022480\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/wEvpzsFW4MY?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EALL ABOARD THE HYPE TRAIN! CHOO CHOO\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENice ambience!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-28T21:17:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E[removed because it should just die apparently]\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-02-28T23:20:05Z\u0022 title=\u002202/28/2015 11:20  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 28, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by GregroxMun\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NovaSilisko","CreatedById":3897,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-28T22:58:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022GregroxMun\u0022 data-cite=\u0022GregroxMun\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://pastebin.com/3vvjushy\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://pastebin.com/3vvjushy\u003C/a\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u0022Another game entirely.\u0022\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIs this then the explaination, at least partially, for that alieny-starbuildy-thing?\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI do wish that would die and be forgotten already. The backstory in SotS is very different than that rambling thing.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Whirligig Girl","CreatedById":36077,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-02-28T23:17:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NovaSilisko\u0022 data-cite=\u0022NovaSilisko\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EI do wish that would die and be forgotten already. The backstory in SotS is very different than that rambling thing.\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI would like to inquire, what\u0027s so bad about it?\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222015-02-28T23:20:14Z\u0022 title=\u002202/28/2015 11:20  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00229 yr\u0022\u003EFebruary 28, 2015\u003C/time\u003E by GregroxMun\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"hotmailcompany52","CreatedById":21696,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-03-01T09:58:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NovaSilisko\u0022 data-cite=\u0022NovaSilisko\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ESNIP\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThat video looks pretty awesome! I presume that was rendered in realtime? If so how performance intensive is it going to be?\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}